      <title>中国演习后台湾军方警告液化天然气存在脆弱性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/taiwan-military-warns-on-lng-vulnerability-after-china-s-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾国防部长表示，如果中国有朝一日实施封锁，台湾的液化天然气进口可能会受到影响 — — 这凸显了北京的军事活动引起台北的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/taiwan-military-warns-on-lng-vulnerability-after-china-s-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 04:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟呼吁建立情报机构应对外部威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/eu-urged-to-create-intelligence-body-to-counter-external-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩要求提交的一份最新报告草案，欧盟应逐步建立一个成熟的情报机构，以更好地应对来自外国势力的威胁，并对境内的间谍活动作出更有力的反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/eu-urged-to-create-intelligence-body-to-counter-external-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平与莫迪将在边界协议达成两年后举行首次会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/xi-modi-to-hold-first-talks-in-two-years-after-border-consensus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平和印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪将于周三举行自 2022 年以来的首次双边会晤。本周早些时候，两国缓解了长达四年的边境僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/xi-modi-to-hold-first-talks-in-two-years-after-border-consensus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 03:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩在美国大选前几周访问洲际弹道导弹基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/kim-jong-un-visits-icbm-base-weeks-ahead-of-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统大选前几周，朝鲜领导人金正恩视察了战略导弹基地，并命令军队“随时”准备对敌人进行反击，此举显然是为了提升其影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/kim-jong-un-visits-icbm-base-weeks-ahead-of-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 01:21:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将亚洲、欧洲汽车排除在汽车减税计划之外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/trump-excludes-asian-european-cars-from-vehicle-tax-break-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普宣扬他为购车提供税收减免的承诺，并强调该优惠只适用于在美国制造的汽车，因为距离选举日仅剩两周，他在一个关键的摇摆州团结选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/trump-excludes-asian-european-cars-from-vehicle-tax-break-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 01:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯支持最低工资 15 美元，与特朗普争夺薪酬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/harris-backs-15-minimum-wage-in-fight-with-trump-over-wages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯支持将联邦最低工资提高到至少每小时 15 美元，并表示她将敦促立法者贯彻落实，因为她试图在工薪阶层选民中巩固自己在经济方面的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/harris-backs-15-minimum-wage-in-fight-with-trump-over-wages</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 00:07:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称特朗普干预选举的说法不会损害两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/trump-accuses-labour-party-of-election-interference-in-complaint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，如果前总统唐纳德·特朗普下个月赢得美国大选，那么他针对工党涉嫌干预选举而提出的法律投诉不会危及他们之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/trump-accuses-labour-party-of-election-interference-in-complaint</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 23:58:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州最高法院拒绝恢复手工计票规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/georgia-supreme-court-refuses-to-revive-ballot-hand-count-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佐治亚州最高法院驳回了共和党在最后一刻提出的恢复一系列新选举规则的要求，其中包括要求在即将到来的美国总统竞选中手工计票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/georgia-supreme-court-refuses-to-revive-ballot-hand-count-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 23:48:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦财政部长认为中国债务谈判“令人鼓舞”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦财政部长表示，巴基斯坦关于延长“一带一路”贷款期限的请求得到了中国的积极回应，这意味着过去因高昂借贷成本而陷入困境的国家可能将获得更多喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 19:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>领事馆爆炸事件引发缅甸局势混乱 习近平面临两难境地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/xi-faces-dilemma-as-consulate-blast-sparks-fear-of-myanmar-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几十年来，中国一直试图在缅甸边境地区无法无天的少数民族武装团体中保持影响力，同时还为缅甸的军事领导人提供支持。上周发生的中国领事馆袭击事件表明，这种平衡行为已经难以维持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/xi-faces-dilemma-as-consulate-blast-sparks-fear-of-myanmar-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 11:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
